### Discovery — Men's Scoreboard, March 16 (Selection Sunday)
# discoverTournamentId() scans these dates looking for NCAA Tournament events.
# Run these in order until you find events[].competitions[].tournament.id (or leagues[].tournament.id).
# Copy that ID into http-client.env.json as mens_tournament_id / womens_tournament_id.

GET https://site.api.espn.com/apis/site/v2/sports/basketball/mens-college-basketball/scoreboard?groups=50&limit=100&dates=20260316
Accept: application/json

